      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/2/51/266",
      "text": [
        "أَمَّا بَعْدُ، فَإِنَّ مَنْ لَمْ يَحْذَرْ مَا هُوَ صَائِرٌ إِلَيْهِ لَمْ يُقَدِّمْ لِنَفْسِهِ مَا يُحْرِزُهَا."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "So now, he who does not fear where he is going, does not send forward for himself that which could protect him."
        ]
      }
    },
    "verse_translations": [
      "en.sayed-ali-raza"
    ]
